<view class="{{['page', z]}}"><view class="header"><text class="header__title">别让你的脑生锈</text><view wx:if="{{a}}" class="streak-pill" bindtap="{{c}}"><text class="streak-pill__fire">🔥</text><text class="streak-pill__num">{{b}} 天连续</text></view></view><text class="date-label">{{d}}</text><view wx:if="{{e}}" class="loading-wrap"><text class="loading-wrap__text">题目加载中...</text></view><view wx:elif="{{f}}" class="empty-wrap"><text class="empty-wrap__emoji">📭</text><text class="empty-wrap__text">今日暂无题目</text><text class="empty-wrap__sub">明天再来看看吧</text></view><block wx:else><view class="train-eyebrow"><text class="train-eyebrow__label">今日大脑训练</text><text class="train-eyebrow__meta">{{g}} · {{h}}</text></view><view class="q-card"><view class="q-card__tag-row"><text class="tag tag--green">{{i}}</text><view class="q-card__right"><view class="q-card__dots"><view wx:for="{{j}}" wx:for-item="i" wx:key="a" class="{{['q-card__dot', i.b && 'q-card__dot--filled']}}"/></view><text wx:if="{{k}}" class="done-badge">✓ 已完成</text></view></view><text class="q-card__body" user-select>{{l}}</text><image wx:if="{{m}}" class="q-card__image" src="{{n}}" mode="widthFix"/></view><view class="{{['draft-preview', s && 'draft-preview--done']}}" bindtap="{{t}}"><text class="draft-preview__hint">{{o}}</text><view wx:if="{{p}}" class="draft-preview__secondary" catchtap="{{q}}"><text>回顾草稿</text></view><view wx:else class="draft-preview__secondary" catchtap="{{r}}"><text>已有思路？直接填写答案</text></view></view><view class="stats-hint"><view wx:if="{{v}}" class="stats-hint__row"><text class="stats-hint__key">连续思考</text><text class="stats-hint__val">{{w}} 天 🔥</text></view><view wx:if="{{x}}" class="stats-hint__row"><text class="stats-hint__key">最近训练</text><view class="stats-hint__dims"><text wx:for="{{y}}" wx:for-item="dim" wx:key="b" class="stats-hint__dim">{{dim.a}}</text></view></view></view></block></view>